channel.title: New Beginnings - LP [The Remixes]
channel.description:
Hey everyone.
Recently, I uploaded an LP called ‚ÄúNew Beginnings‚Äù. So, I‚Äôve decided to do a remix contest for the LP.
**INFO [UPDATED]** Before, I chose to judge each track remix separately. Now, I will be choosing the 8 best remix submissions shared in this thread.
In order to enter, simply ping me in the forums here or DM me via Auxy Disco what track(s) you would like to remix. Try to be patient when I reply back, as I do have real life stuff to deal with as well.
**LP LINK** * [New Beginnings - LP](https://soundcloud.com/greyoldtwit/sets/new-beginnings-lp)
**TRACK LINKS** * [New Beginnings](https://soundcloud.com/greyoldtwit/new-beginnings) * [Metropolitan](https://soundcloud.com/greyoldtwit/metropolitan) * [Fireflies (with Jelm√∏](https://soundcloud.com/jelmo_music/fireflies) * [Dreams](https://soundcloud.com/greyoldtwit/dreams) * [Last Stars (with paroxyzm)](https://soundcloud.com/paroxyzm-music/last-stars-with-greyoldtwit) * [Remembrance](https://soundcloud.com/greyoldtwit/remembrance) * [Far Blue (with Sylent)](https://soundcloud.com/greyoldtwit/far-blue-with-sylent) * [Memory](https://soundcloud.com/greyoldtwit/memory)
**JUDGES** @GreyOldTwit [Main Judge] @anon34001995 [Co-Judge] @Sylent [Co-Judge] @paroxyzm [Co-Judge] @tictacto [Co-Judge]
NOTE TO JUDGES: *Judges are allowed to participate, but they will judge fairly (and I will be checking to make sure).*
**CHANCES OF WINNING** As there is eight tracks, there will be eight winners for the remix contest (one for each track remix). The winner will be determined by me (and my fellow co-judges)
**PRIZE** The winning remixes will be added onto a seperate LP; which will be posted publicly on SoundCloud and posted on Spotify, Apple Music and Google Play Music.
**RULES** 1. The track needs to last for a minimum of 2 minutes. (I will accept the track if it‚Äôs up to 5 seconds short from minimum requirement).
2. You are allowed to remix more than one track (however, only one of your remixes can win).
3. Your submission(s) are required to be on SoundCloud (Share the link on this thread and ping me).
4. You are allowed to use your own cover art, when you post your track.
**DEADLINE** You will all have until the 24th of May (Australian Central [and my Birthday üéÅ]) to submit you remixes.
**PARTICIPANTS:**
[details="Participant List‚Äù] Jelm√∏ - Far Blue (Submitted) FRUDS - Metropolitan (Submitted) Aykut - Last Stars The_Osprey - Memory surf - Remembrance Mr Mooo - Remembrance (Submitted) Weeaboo_Jones - Last Stars Tolberto - Dreams polezer0 - Dreams & Last Stars (Submitted) BeeUrSelf - Fireflies T3CH - New Beginnings & Metropolitan XLXK - New Beginnings [/details]
**FINAL MESSAGE** If anything above doesn‚Äôt make sense, let me know. Good luck to everyone. ~ GreyOldTwit

item.title: New Beginnings - LP [The Remixes]
item.dc:creator: GR3Y
item.description:
It‚Äôs Friday, judges are finished judging and we are ready to share. All comments were summaries of what the judges and I stated when judging the tracks. One more thing; the late-submission period is now over. Feel free to remix any of the tracks in the LP, but the remixes will not be on the ‚ÄòNew Beginnings - The Remixes (LP)‚Äô. Right‚Ä¶ time for the results.

3rd Place - @polezer0 [Last Stars Remix]

The changes made were well done. It works very well. The only downside, which was pointed out by 3 of our judges, was the time it took to get to the drop. There were points in the track that could have been great for a drop, but never occurred.

2nd Place - @FRUDS [Metropolitan Remix]

The changes to this track is nice. A faster version of the track with the recognisable piano from the original track. There wasn‚Äôt much comments made for this remix from the judges.

1st Place - @Mr_Mooo [Remembrance Remix]

This remix‚Ä¶ was amazing. It feels more like a reinvented track rather than a remix. Completely changing the track, but has hints of originality in the remix. Overall, impressive.
